<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>IgniteVR Overlays</title>


  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/styles.css">


</head>

<body>

  <div class="text_content">
    <h1 align="center">List of IgniteVR overlays.</h1>

    <p>Most overlays require &lt;?client_name=USERNAME&gt; to retrieve the correct data.</p>
    <p>Overlays require the OBS source to be set to 1920x1080 unless otherwise specified.</p>

    <h2>VRML</h2>
    <h3>Echo Arena</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/match_setup">/match_setup</a>
        <ul>
          <li>Contains a list of upcoming matches. Click on one to set the team name and logo for the rest of the
            overlays.</li>
          <li>Has an input field for client name.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><a href="/casterdesk">/casterdesk</a> Caster Desk
        <ul>
          <li>An overview of the current match. Contains previous matches by both teams and detailed game stats.</li>
          <li>Has an input field for client name.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><a href="/group_recent_matches">/group_recent_matches</a> Group Recent Matches
        <ul>
          <li>A list of recent matches, with the ability to hide or split data from certain rounds. Used to verify data
            before it appears in the scoreboard overlays.</li>
          <li>Parameter(s): client_name, series_name</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><a href="/prematch_overlay">/prematch_overlay</a>
        <ul>
          <li>Shows a list of player names for both teams near the botton of the screen.</li>
          <li>Parameter(s): client_name, series_name</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><a href="/prematch_overlay_old">/prematch_overlay_old</a>
        <ul>
          <li>Team vs Team at the top center, left and right sidebars with team logos, mmr, division, and player names
          </li>
          <li>Parameter(s): client_name, series_name</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><a href="/midmatch_overlay">/midmatch_overlay</a>
        <ul>
          <li>Team names and logos at the top of the screen</li>
          <li>Parameter(s): client_name, series_name</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><a href="/prematch_overlay_2">/prematch_overlay_2</a>
        <ul>
          <li>Team names, logos, division, mmr, and record at the bottom of the screen</li>
          <li>Parameter(s): client_name, series_name</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><a href="/most_recent_match">/most_recent_match</a>
        <ul>
          <li>Old style player and team stats at the bottom of the screen. Team stats are on the sides.</li>
          <li>Parameter(s): client_name, series_name, live</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><a href="/all_recent_matches">/all_recent_matches</a>
        <ul>
          <li>List of recent rounds with time, caster, and scores
          </li>
          <li>Parameter(s): series_name (optional: if not specified, shows all series)</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><a href="/fastest_jousts">/fastest_jousts</a>
        <ul>
          <li>List of fastest joust time events recorded
          </li>
          <li>Parameter(s): series_name (optional: if not specified, shows all series)</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><a href="/scoreboard">/scoreboard</a>
        <ul>
          <li>New style player and team stats at the bottom of the screen. Team stats are on the bottom.</li>
          <li>Parameter(s): client_name, series_name, live</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Onward</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/match_setup_onward">/match_setup_onward</a>
        <ul>
          <li>Contains a list of upcoming matches. Click on one to set the team name and logo for the rest of the
            overlays.</li>
          <li>Has an input field for client name.</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><a href="/midmatch_overlay_onward">/midmatch_overlay_onward</a>
        <ul>
          <li>Has team names and logos</li>
          <li>Parameter(s): client_name, series_name</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>CVRE</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/match_awards">/match_awards</a>
        <ul>
          <li>Shows a series of custom match awards</li>
          <li>Parameter(s): client_name, series_name</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><a href="/cvre_stats_blue">/cvre_stats_blue</a>
        <ul>
          <li>Shows player and team stats.</li>
          <li>This overlay source should be set to 750x360 instead of 1920x1080 and then positionally adjusted with OBS
          </li>
          <li>To increase the size even further, "body { font-size: 1.5em; }" can be used as a css override. The source
            resolution should also be changed. The default font-size is 1.5em</li>
          <li>Parameter(s): client_name, series_name</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li><a href="/cvre_stats_orange">/cvre_stats_orange</a>
        <ul>
          <li>Shows player and team stats.</li>
          <li>This overlay source should be set to 750x360 instead of 1920x1080 and then positionally adjusted with OBS
          </li>
          <li>To increase the size even further, "body { font-size: 1.5em; }" can be used as a css override. The source
            resolution should also be changed. The default font-size is 1.5em</li>
          <li>Parameter(s): client_name, series_name</li>
        </ul>
      </li>

    </ul>
  </div>
</body>

</html>